      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Ihsääks fehje tamni\nSemmê/ un dabhuja tanni Gad-\ndā/ fiuntkahrtigus Anglus/jo tas\nKUNGS swehtija to.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas Wihrs ange augnu-\nmâ / un tappe leels / teekams\nwiꞥſch tohti angsts ktuä.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tam bij Manta no fih-\nkeim / un Manta no leelem Loh-\npeem / un dands Saines / un tee\nWihlistexi ſkande winnu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiſſas Akkas/ ko wiꞥ-\nnā Tehwa Kalpt / winna Tehwa\nAhbrääma Laikā bij rakfufchi /\ntahs aisbahfe tee Wihlistexi / un\npildija tahs ar Smiltim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Abimeleks fazzija arri-\ndsan us Ihsääku : Eij nohst no\nmuuns / jo tu effi dands wairak\nwarrens tappis/ ne kā mehs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad aisgahje Ihsaaks no\nturrenes/ un nolaidahs eekſch Ge-\nraras Eelejas/ un dshwoja tur.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Ihsääks usrakfe attat\ntahs Uhdens Akkas / ko tee winna\nTehwa Ahbrääma Laikā bij rak-\nfufchi/ un tee Wihlistexi/ pehz/ ka\nAhbrääms nomirris/ bij aisbah-\nsufchi / un wiꞥſch noſauze winno\nWahrdus pehz teem Wahrdeem/\nar ko tahs winna Tehws bij no-\nfauzis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Ihsääka Kalpi rakfe\neekſch tahs Eelejas / un atradde\ntur weennu Akku ar dshwu uh-\ndeni.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad bahrahs tee Geraras\nGanni ar Ihsaika Ganneem/faz-\nzidami: fchis Uhdens muuns pee-\nDerr/ tad noſauze wiꞥſch tahs Ak-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "kas Wahrdn Eseku / tape-\ntee arwinnu bij bahruſchees\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad rakfe tee zittu\nun tee bahrahs pahr to arr\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "tapehz noſauze wiꞥſch w\nWahrdn Sitna.\nUn wiꞥſch zeblahs n\nnenes/ un rakfe zittu Akku /\nne bahrahs pahr to / tad n\nwiꞥſch winnas Wahrdn Rei\nun fazzija : Jo nu ir\nKUNGS nuhs isplattijie\nmehs effam anglojuſchees f\nSemmê.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad gahje wiꞥſch n\nnenes angſcham us Bersabu\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas KUNGS\njahs winnam tanni Nak-\nfazzija: Es effim Ahbrääma\nTehwa DEews/ ne bihstces\nesmu ar tew / un fwehtischu\nun wairoſchu tawu Dsimu\nAhbrääma manna Kalpa de\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch ustaisi\nweenu Altari / un peefa\nKUNGA Wahrdn / un u\ntur fatvu Dshwofti/un J\nKalpi rakfe tur weennu Akku\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Abimeleks gahje\nno Geraras / un weens no n\nDraugeem Aüſats un P\nwinna Kaxxa Spehka\nneeks.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Ihsää\nteem : Kapehz nahkat juh-\nman / kas juhe man eenih\nun effat mann no fewis n\nnuſchi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tee fazzija : Me-\ndseht redsam/ ka tas KUNG\n"
    }
  ],
